comment:
* A listener type for receiving notification on IMS call session events.
     * When an event is generated for an {@link IImsCallSession},
     * the application is notified by having one of the methods called on
     * the {@link IImsCallSessionListener}.

methods.name: public void callSessionInitiating(ImsCallProfile profile)
methods.comment: * Notifies the result of the basic session operation (setup / terminate).

methods.name: public void callSessionHeld(ImsCallProfile profile)
methods.comment: * Notifies the result of the call hold/resume operation.

methods.name: public void callSessionMergeStarted(IImsCallSession newSession, ImsCallProfile profile)
methods.comment:
* Notifies the start of a call merge operation.
         *
         * @param newSession The merged call session.
         * @param profile The call profile.

methods.name: public void callSessionMergeComplete(IImsCallSession newSession)
methods.comment:
* Notifies the successful completion of a call merge operation.
         *
         * @param newSession The call session.

methods.name: public void callSessionMergeFailed(ImsReasonInfo reasonInfo)
methods.comment:
* Notifies of a failure to perform a call merge operation.
         *
         * @param reasonInfo The merge failure reason.

methods.name: public void callSessionUpdated(ImsCallProfile profile)
methods.comment: * Notifies the result of call upgrade / downgrade or any other call updates.

methods.name: public void callSessionConferenceExtended(IImsCallSession newSession, ImsCallProfile profile)
methods.comment: * Notifies the result of conference extension.

methods.name: public void callSessionInviteParticipantsRequestDelivered()
methods.comment:
* Notifies the result of the participant invitation / removal to/from
         * the conference session.

methods.name: public void callSessionConferenceStateUpdated(ImsConferenceState state)
methods.comment: * Notifies the changes of the conference info. in the conference session.

methods.name: public void callSessionUssdMessageReceived(int mode, String ussdMessage)
methods.comment: * Notifies the incoming USSD message.

methods.name: public void callSessionMayHandover(int srcNetworkType, int targetNetworkType)
methods.comment:
* Notifies of a case where a {@link ImsCallSession} may
         * potentially handover from one radio technology to another.
         * @param srcNetworkType The source network type; one of the network type constants defined
         *                       in {@link android.telephony.TelephonyManager}.  For example
         *                      {@link android.telephony.TelephonyManager#NETWORK_TYPE_LTE}.
         * @param targetNetworkType The target radio access technology; one of the network type
         *                          constants defined in {@link android.telephony.TelephonyManager}.
         *                          For example
         *                          {@link android.telephony.TelephonyManager#NETWORK_TYPE_LTE}.

methods.name: public void callSessionHandover(int srcNetworkType, int targetNetworkType, ImsReasonInfo reasonInfo)
methods.comment: * Notifies of handover information for this call

methods.name: public void callSessionHandoverFailed(int srcNetworkType, int targetNetworkType, ImsReasonInfo reasonInfo)
methods.comment: * Notifies of handover failure info for this call

methods.name: public void callSessionTtyModeReceived(int mode)
methods.comment: * Notifies the TTY mode received from remote party.

methods.name: public void callSessionMultipartyStateChanged(boolean isMultiParty)
methods.comment:
* Notifies of a change to the multiparty state for this {@code ImsCallSession}.
         *
         * @param isMultiParty {@code true} if the session became multiparty, {@code false}
         *      otherwise.

methods.name: public void callSessionRttModifyRequestReceived(ImsCallProfile callProfile)
methods.comment: * Received RTT modify request from remote party

methods.name: public void callSessionRttModifyResponseReceived(int status)
methods.comment: * Received response for RTT modify request

methods.name: public void callSessionRttMessageReceived(String rttMessage)
methods.comment: * RTT Message received

methods.name: public void callSessionRttAudioIndicatorChanged(ImsStreamMediaProfile profile)
methods.comment: * While in call, there has been a change in RTT audio indicator.

methods.name: public void callSessionDtmfReceived(char dtmf)
methods.comment:
* DTMF digit received.
         * @param dtmf The DTMF digit.

methods.name: public void callQualityChanged(CallQuality callQuality)
methods.comment: * Call quality updated

methods.name: public void callSessionRtpHeaderExtensionsReceived(@NonNull List<RtpHeaderExtension> extensions)
methods.comment:
* RTP header extension data received.
         * @param extensions The header extension data.

methods.name: public void callSessionSendAnbrQuery(int mediaType, int direction, int bitsPerSecond)
methods.comment:
* ANBR Query received.
         *
         * @param mediaType MediaType is used to identify media stream such as audio or video.
         * @param direction Direction of this packet stream (e.g. uplink or downlink).
         * @param bitsPerSecond This value is the bitrate requested by the other party UE through
         *        RTP CMR, RTCPAPP or TMMBR, and ImsStack converts this value to the MAC bitrate
         *        (defined in TS36.321, range: 0 ~ 8000 kbit/s).

methodNames: public void callSessionMergeStarted(IImsCallSession newSession, ImsCallProfile profile)
public void callSessionUssdMessageReceived(int mode, String ussdMessage)
public void callSessionMayHandover(int srcNetworkType, int targetNetworkType)
public void callSessionHandover(int srcNetworkType, int targetNetworkType, ImsReasonInfo reasonInfo)
public void callSessionHandoverFailed(int srcNetworkType, int targetNetworkType, ImsReasonInfo reasonInfo)
public void callSessionSendAnbrQuery(int mediaType, int direction, int bitsPerSecond)
